data.description: Gorgeous all brick home with convenient access to interstate, shopping and restaurants. Spacious great room boasts cathedral ceiling with stone fireplace. Large eat-in kitchen with LOTS of cabinet space, island and pantry. Formal Dining with coffered ceiling. Primary bedroom features tray ceiling, large closet, and ensuite with separate shower/tub and double vanities. Custom walled patio, perfect for entertaining.
